EXTRACTED VALUE: Blue Dragon is a good RPG; it is just not a great one.
Mercenaries 2 is arguably a bigger and more ambitious game than the original, but it feels less polished and less satisfying.
Few World War II video games are as gripping and brutal as Brothers in Arms: Hell's Highway.
The game is definitely over-priced. With that said, this is still one of the most engaging new multiplayer-only games out there.
